<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <p xml:id="Aink132-kilavi">
        āṟṟāmai vāyilākap pukuntirunta talaimakaṟkup pāṇaṉ vantuḻi talaimakaḷ colliyatu</p>    <p xml:lang="en">
          Said by the heroine when the bard came for [= on behalf of] the hero who had entered, unable to bear [the wait], through the entrance.
 </p>
 </div> 
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink139">
<l>amma vāḻi koṇka vemvayiṉ</l>
<l>māṇala maruṭṭu niṉṉiṉum</l>
<l>pāṇa ṉallōr nalañcitaik kummē</l>
</lg>
<lg xml:lang="en">
  <l>Oh man from the maritime tract! </l>
    <l>The bard makes waste the beauty of beautiful girls </l>
      <l>Even more than you who disturbs our glorious beauty.</l>
</lg>
    </div>
